{
  "stem": "3040.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was taking over the factory on behalf of the German government.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had absolutely nothing to say in this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He had his papers, and this was what he was going to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then I was talking to him, because I spoke a little German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then I asked him where he stays, where he lives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in the evening, I visited him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I didn't wear my armband.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I took it off and tried to reason with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And told him the following.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Here, this is a chocolate factory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You are dependent on production.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You're dependent on raw materials, which are not readily available in Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Not in any place that you are, not in Germany even.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because chocolate is produced, if you know, from cocoa beans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This is kind of a bean like coffee beans, only it's called a cocoa bean.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This is the basis for production of chocolate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You roast them, and you grind them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then you also use the butter that you extract from these cocoa beans, it's called cocoa butter.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this is, in combination with sugar, you make chocolate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said here, you have maybe two weeks supply of raw materials.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What are you going to do later?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You'll be out of a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I gave him some money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said forget about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I saved our factory for another few months until we are able to produce what we have, and we lived on it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He let me continue because he saw the logic of what I told him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he was looking for another better job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, he could get anything he wanted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then this was already in the summer of 1940.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
